   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=360.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Mana Regeneration</span><hr size=1> Hi all. I have a few things to say about the magician's mana regen. Almost everything about the mage class is perfect. We got the xp penalty nerfed, and a few more things that were annoying, but IMO, we need some kind of mana regen ability. Enchanters get clarity, necromancer's get call of bones, lich, etc... and shaman's get cannibalize. Druids get wolf form and sow, and wizards get familiars. My main is a 53 mage, and I actually meditate longer than I play the game. It's really annoying when it comes to soloing, because of the 5-10 minute pause in between. I see necro's and shaman's chain pulling and leveling up twice as fast as I do. So, I'm not trying to start any flame wars here, just post your comments and suggestions please <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubalanzsonofanz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Abuser of EZCodes</span><br>  Posts: 1924<br> <font color=#333333>(9/26/02 5:35:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=360.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Regeneration</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> My main is a 53 mage, and I actually meditate longer than I play the game.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
