</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mana Regeneration</span><hr size=1> Reclaiming pets is not the correct answer. I doubt when they built the mage class, they did it around reclaiming pets (to gain mana) and chain casting (to kill mobs). Those are tricks that have been developed by players and which IMO are not part of the mage class. They actually are hurting the mage class because now they take them into account when they make new spells / abilities.<br>
<br>
I think the way they desined the mage class is:<br>
Keep your pet alive as long as possible<br>
Meditate to regen mana<br>
<br>
This is the way it should be. Relay on your equip and not on 200 bags of malachite. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uomegasyphon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>omegasyphon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 439<br> <font color=#333333>(9/27/02 1:32:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=360.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   comment</span><hr size=1> well that is the theory but are pets cant last that long for us to do that, course kei is so cheap these days and abundant to <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uglasya7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glasya7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 229<br> <font color=#333333>(9/27/02 6:27:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=360.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: comment</span><hr size=1> Transon's is a nice mana regen spell you get at like 57 or 58 (been a while).  Your best bet is to get Regen3 and a regen item (zland heart, aura of battle effect, etc) and mod rod self to regen mana.  Even better is to 2box a healer and heal/regen yourself after rodding; or 2box a chanter.  Not the most convenient way but it works.<br>
